{"tid":1755842,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拉過驚累到女朋友應該點做好","createTime":"2019-11-25T19:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T12:23:01.000Z","uid":221202,"like":8,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"623b25f0de7b80fe1ebc8ce899198284f4cf081b","tid":1755842,"uid":221202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T19:20:30.000Z","msg":"介紹吓背景先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n      我同我女朋友喺呢三個月做&rsquo;運動&rsquo;識嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我喺同佢拍拖第一個月嘅紀念日衰撚左，過一個月之後又衰咗多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我係一開始就同佢啲朋友講過話：如果我有咩事同佢講唔使等我咁樣.<br />\n之後出返嚟先知道，佢答返佢啲friend佢點都唔會放棄我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n        但係問題嚟喇，佢生得又靚讀書又好，我就兩樣都一般般仲要依家衰埋.我自己明知我未必比到好嘅嘢佢，但係佢唔肯飛我，我又唔忍心要佢辛苦，到底我應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd34fa3fc8ffdd437b060619529dc159089f258","tid":1755842,"uid":221202,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T19:21:08.000Z","msg":"Btw 唔好上熱門 呢啲唔係咩有用資訊"},{"pid":"03f6401a05a26c5bcbba640c968b71e40c6138be","tid":1755842,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T19:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07708a6bd103266cc08ede3b31d512919206f384","tid":1755842,"uid":136061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T19:22:19.000Z","msg":"好好對佢"},{"pid":"c0f0486978bc0ae2e341b1b0bb47a07a85a1c697","tid":1755842,"uid":311563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T19:24:23.000Z","msg":"對佢好啲啦，咁嘅女朋友真係好難得㗎，巴打好好珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515f2a2166929fa8ac0d0d0d90b4283f3e20a7b0","tid":1755842,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T19:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" clas